Identified entries
Starting from the bottom of the diagram:

A = 1110 (14 in decimal)
B = 0100 (2 in decimal)
Therefore, we perform the following:
1110 + 0100 = 10010

But the circuit only displays the 4 least significant bits . So we only read: 0010 on the 4 output bits .

